Package io.github.tonywasher.joceanus.tethys.core.button

Class TethysUICoreListButtonManager<T extends Comparable<? super T>>

java.lang.Object
io.github.tonywasher.joceanus.tethys.core.base.TethysUICoreComponent
io.github.tonywasher.joceanus.tethys.core.button.TethysUICoreListButtonManager<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the object type
All Implemented Interfaces:
OceanusEventRegistrar.OceanusEventProvider<TethysUIEvent>, TethysUIComponent, TethysUIListButtonManager<T>, TethysUIControl.TethysUIListButton<T>
public abstract class TethysUICoreListButtonManager<T extends Comparable<? super T>> extends TethysUICoreComponent implements TethysUIListButtonManager<T>
ListButton Manager.

Provides the following events.

NEWVALUE
fired when the dialog is closed with new values selected.
Detail is the new set of values.
EDITFOCUSLOST
fired when the dialog is cancelled without a value being selected.
